Landing Page Animation Details

Entrance Animations: Fade-in, slide-in, scale-up, rotate
Scroll Animations: Reveal on scroll, parallax, stagger animations
Hover Effects: Scale, color change, shadow, lift
Micro-interactions: Button ripple effect, icon bounce, text shimmer
Smooth Transitions: All animations use easing functions (ease-in-out, cubic-bezier)
Performance: Use Intersection Observer for scroll-triggered animations
Mobile Optimized: Reduced animations on mobile devices, respects prefers-reduced-motion


