Core Features

QR Code Generation

Input field to accept text, URLs, or any data
Real-time QR code preview that updates instantly
Support for various data types (URLs, text, email, phone, WiFi, vCard, SMS)
Error handling with user-friendly messages


Customization Options

Size Control: Adjustable dimensions (preset + custom)
Color Picker: Custom foreground and background colors
Error Correction Level: Select L, M, Q, or H
Border/Margin: Adjustable quiet zone
Style Options: Different QR code patterns (standard, dots, rounded)


Download & Export

Download as PNG, SVG, JPEG
Copy to clipboard (as image or data URL)
Print functionality
Bulk download option


Preset Templates

Website URL, Email, Phone, WiFi, vCard, SMS
Quick-fill forms with validation
One-click generation


History & Management

Recent QR codes stored in localStorage
Thumbnail previews
Quick actions (re-download, modify, delete)
Clear history option


User Interface

Responsive design (desktop, tablet, mobile)
Dark/Light mode toggle
Live preview pane
Settings panel with smooth transitions
Intuitive layout with clear sections



Technical Requirements

Build Tool: Vite for fast development
Framework: React with hooks
QR Code Library: qrcode.react or qr-code-styling
Styling: Tailwind CSS + CSS animations
Animations: Framer Motion for complex animations
Icons: Lucide React
State Management: React Context or Zustand
Code Quality: Clean, modular components

